'''苏霍伊КР-860'''（俄罗斯之翼）<ref>{{cite news |last=Litovkin |first=Dmitry |title=Interview with Mikhail Simonov - the inventor of the Sukhoi jet fighters |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sponsored/russianow/6453948/Russia-Now-Interview-with-Mikhail-Simonov---the-inventor-of-the-Sukhoi-jet-fighters.html |work=Russia Now |publisher=[[Rossiyskaya_Gazeta|Rossiyskaya Gazeta]] |date=28 October 20a prop09 |accessdate=27 November 2009 |archive-date=2009-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091031074822/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sponsored/russianow/6453948/Russia-Now-Interview-with-Mikhail-Simonov---the-inventor-of-the-Sukhoi-jet-fighters.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，早先被命名为скд-171，是一种由[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[联合航空制造公司|联合航空制造公司]][[苏霍伊|苏霍伊]]提出的宽体喷气式飞机构想。<ref>{{cite news |last=Kingsley-Jones |first=Max |title=Giant dreams |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/1999/12/22/59888/giant-dreams.html |work=[[Flight_International|Flight International]] |date=22 December 1999 |accessdate=27 November 2009 |archive-date=2019-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208091659/http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/1999/12/22/59888/giant-dreams.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==发展==
该机被设计为最高重量650吨，有效载荷300吨，主飞行甲板有三通道和每排12个座位，上层甲板为双通道和每排9个座位，被设计为有能力运载860到1000名乘客。 相比之下 [[安-225|安-225]] 最大重量600吨，有效载荷250吨。 一个1比24的模型被展示<ref>{{cite news |title=Sukhoi displays 900-seater concept |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/1999/06/23/53257/sukhoi-displays-900-seater-concept.html |work=[[Flight_International|Flight International]] |date=23 June 1999 |accessdate=27 November 2009 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.testpilot.ru/russia/sukhoi/kr/860/images/kr860_5.jpg |title=存档副本 |access-date=2013-08-31 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030223757/http://www.testpilot.ru/russia/sukhoi/kr/860/images/kr860_5.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.testpilot.ru/russia/sukhoi/kr/860/images/kr-860a.jpg |title=存档副本 |access-date=2013-08-31 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309202011/http://testpilot.ru/russia/sukhoi/kr/860/images/kr-860a.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref> 于1999年的[[巴黎航展|巴黎航展]]<ref>{{cite book |title=Jane's all the world's aircraft |editor=Jackson, Paul |year=2001 |publisher=[[Jane's_Information_Group|Jane's Information Group]] |isbn=978-0-7106-2307-2 |page=450 }}</ref>。如果这种飞机被顺利制造，那么它将成为世界上最大，最宽和最重的客机<ref>{{cite news |last=Reeves |first=Phil |title=Russia plans to build world's largest passenger airliner |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4913001.html |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=17 April 1998 |accessdate=27 November 2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102151103/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4913001.html |archive-date=2012-11-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

飞机概念起源于1990年代的一个花费100亿美元（早前披露为40-55亿美元）的预想项目，要求在2000年前制造。 飞机单价约为1.6-2亿美元，预计有300架的市场规模，计划于[[喀山飞机制造联盟|喀山飞机制造联盟]]的厂房制造。最初被设计为载客，后来КР-860т版被设计为空中（т意为载油)[[液化天然气|液化天然气]] 运载机。因该飞机运载液化天然气，该设计被预想使用液化天然气为其涡轮发动机，以取代普通的[[航油|航油]]， 如在[[图-204#Tu-206|图-206]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tupolev.ru/English/Show.asp?SectionID=82&Page=2 |title=PSC "Tupolev" – Cryogenic aircraft |publisher=Tupolev.ru |date= |accessdate=2010-11-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126222743/http://www.tupolev.ru/English/Show.asp?SectionID=82 |archivedate=2010-11-26 }}</ref>上使用的航油。

该项目却仅限于模型。

